                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13468441" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 3 Oct 2012 09:43:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch for this. The patch also change the default port from 8000 since it&apos;s a bit crowded as a port number.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13468704" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 3 Oct 2012 17:52:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t follow &lt;tt&gt;InetAddress.getByName(StorageService.instance.getRpcaddress(endpoint));&lt;/tt&gt; &amp;#8211; why convert it to a String, to convert back w/ getByName?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13468723" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 3 Oct 2012 18:27:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;endpoint&lt;/tt&gt; is the listen_address of the node, but for event, we want to provide the address on which the node can be joined by a client, hence StorageService.instance.getRpcaddress.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13468856" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 3 Oct 2012 21:29:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Feels a bit hackish but since we&apos;re not doing it in performance critical areas, +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13469241" author="slebresne" created="Thu, 4 Oct 2012 09:12:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
